news.title: Juicy Swapper
news.body:
Welcome, you can now create your own
account for Juicy Swapper! Why create
an account? A Juicy account provid
more options then a guest would have!
if you run into any bugs please
report them to kaede immediately please.
Enjoy using Juicy Swapper and feel free to join
our discord for help.
